{"tid":2021801,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"華為P40Pro混用京東方、LG OLED螢幕再惹爭議，華為粉絲帶顯微鏡買手機：我要買到LG螢幕的手機！","createTime":"2020-05-18T03:14:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T06:00:15.000Z","uid":109923,"like":49,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"3b87492301b9be4939da4b7f708baacc9487a214","tid":2021801,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T03:14:00.000Z","msg":"　　2018年華為發布的mate20 Pro採用LG OLED的版本出現綠mon問題，遭到了消費者的口誅筆伐，中國人分分高潮指京東方的OLED比LG更可靠，以後只支持國產京東方螢幕，永不錄用LG OLED。當然，事實是華為封裝LG OLED螢幕過程出問題，所以邊緣才會出現綠光。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t927O98.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft927O98.jpg&h=64d9fb29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n　　兩年過去了，華為新一代旗艦P40Pro繼續混用京東方、LG的OLED螢幕，然而這次中國人卻想要LG螢幕了...<br />\n<br />\n微博、知乎等網站充斥著「抽到京東方OLED就要求換貨的聲音」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sAwP2Lh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsAwP2Lh.jpg&h=dc69c62f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ucm09ow.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fucm09ow.png&h=dae88e8a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ej0k9rt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fej0k9rt.jpg&h=6c191357&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有人總結出華為的策略：較受歡迎的銀色機身則較大機會抽到京東方OLED<br />\n螢幕質素不同，價錢卻一樣，華為用較好看的顏色來彌補價差...<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W4q5A3x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW4q5A3x.png&h=52866a4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有網民指出，京東方OLED即使是用淘寶，很多字體邊緣也是模糊、顯示不清晰。玩遊戲的時候遊戲人物的邊緣也較模糊。今年眾多旗艦手機螢幕都在宣傳色彩還原度，然而華為手機的色彩依然偏艷麗，認為是在掩蓋手機螢幕本身的缺點。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TanS0n4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTanS0n4.png&h=180b7a21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一眾預訂華為手機的網民祝願能夠抽到LG的鑽石排列OLED螢幕。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cnAAX9K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcnAAX9K.png&h=cc2c93e4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n亦有人指出華為應仿傚OPPO手機，在包裝上清楚標示LG OLED<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O6qxfWq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO6qxfWq.png&h=c9ac7a98&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　　到底為什麼京東方的OLED較差？因為京東方採用了「周冬雨」的Delta排列方式，京東方的1080p OLED螢幕在華為P30 Pro上已經經過了充分的驗證，素質一般，而且這種排列在1080p分辨率上清晰度也不夠高，與三星、LG OLED螢幕的鑽石Pentile排列有肉眼可見的差距。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qt6Xr8D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQt6Xr8D.jpg&h=661cdcdc&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2dYCr8E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2dYCr8E.jpg&h=391c609c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7DyVYfi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7DyVYfi.jpg&h=6aa5e3af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3mCfYko.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3mCfYko.jpg&h=a6b65600&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eAW8yOE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeAW8yOE.jpg&h=8d9baa65&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MUKibDj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMUKibDj.jpg&h=ca773666&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n  「周冬雨」Delta排列的有效子像素少了三分之一左右。一塊Delta排列的1080P解析率螢幕，等效標準RGB的ppi值大概就是720p，顯示效果相當於LCD螢幕上的720p。 <br />\n<br />\n　　這次華為P40 Pro解析度來到2640x1200之後這種情況會得到緩解，清晰度大概會<strong>跟鑽石Pentile排列的1080P螢幕差不多</strong>，日常使用也足夠清晰，但是LG的螢幕在相同解析度下，質素也會變得更好了啊，這就導致同樣的價錢，買到京東方螢幕的用戶就不願意了。但是在不出現大問題的情況下，官方是不會像Mate 20 Pro那時一樣直接換新機的，華為也沒有這個打算。<br />\n<br />\n　　那麼又有一個問題來了，為什麼京東方不使用鑽石Pentile排列呢？其實京東方已經用過了，早華為P40Pro一個月多上市的小米黑鯊3 Pro手機就用上了鑽石Pentile排列，隨後三星法務上市聯繫，要求停止生產侵權產品。<br />\n<br />\n　　三星在中國早於2013年申請了鑽石排列的專利，20年後才失效（也就是2033年），在專利過期之前沒有三星的專利授權，任何其它廠商不得生產像素排列為「鑽石排列」的OLED螢幕，也就是說，BOE做周冬雨排列的OLED螢幕並不是因為技術原因做不了鑽石排列，而是三星擁有專利導致BOE不能做鑽石排列的螢幕。等到專利過期的時候估計Mini LED/Micro LED已經接替OLED成為主流了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t0pqBa4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft0pqBa4.jpg&h=6a327693&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0qyZFAJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0qyZFAJ.jpg&h=58e8d52e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在韓國政府協調下，LG可以使用鑽石Pentile排列，但像素較三星圓，而三星的像素較方型。"},{"pid":"a9a1cb560872e765ff24c966fb41b976fbc8e729","tid":2021801,"uid":54502,"like":46,"dislike":2,"score":44,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T03:16:10.000Z","msg":"似以前買iPhone 唔要Samsung 晶片，要台積電"},{"pid":"842fa31c4ef03d851053bf9c86fe84432b1bc62e","tid":2021801,"uid":176111,"like":44,"dislike":2,"score":42,"quote":{"pid":"a9a1cb560872e765ff24c966fb41b976fbc8e729","tid":2021801,"uid":54502,"like":46,"dislike":2,"score":44,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T03:16:10.000Z","msg":"似以前買iPhone 唔要Samsung 晶片，要台積電"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T03:20:20.000Z","msg":"似現家買Samsung 唔要 exynos  要snapdragon<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2cda1031082c2249efc41d689ec1babe1594350","tid":2021801,"uid":159870,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T03:25:38.000Z","msg":"咁都關周冬雨事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"600ba07b024cd8c2a2ea599a4d7288065118b772","tid":2021801,"uid":112760,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"842fa31c4ef03d851053bf9c86fe84432b1bc62e","tid":2021801,"uid":176111,"like":44,"dislike":2,"score":42,"quote":{"pid":"a9a1cb560872e765ff24c966fb41b976fbc8e729","tid":2021801,"uid":54502,"like":46,"dislike":2,"score":44,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T03:16:10.000Z","msg":"似以前買iPhone 唔要Samsung 晶片，要台積電"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T03:20:20.000Z","msg":"似現家買Samsung 唔要 exynos  要snapdragon<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2